=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇故仔，好多人都會幾OK，有助spread</span></span></strong>我地情況出去<br />\n5）以後我地本地同外國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣都塞條片的link入去</span></strong></span>，又或者YouTube channel<br />\n<br />\n但廢J我完全不識點樣整呢D片出來，卡通又好真人又好，都唔識，眾籌也沒experience。所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想集結神力，有邊位兄弟覺得有得諗，就幫手spread出去同用力push，小弟廢J P牌仔自push都做唔到</span></span></strong>，sosaad。"},{"pid":"f089d7441c13086ab7e47f3d621a3f50447c3e55","tid":1577141,"uid":137874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:29:55.000Z","msg":"美國開緊會喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國開緊會喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d8abf624fd50cd6cb91f8c8644afb2f673dec1","tid":1577141,"uid":310846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c34e6744753542fdadbf5d7ba6e7e4b9db2d762f","tid":1577141,"uid":167037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96df45b5e8f3815437cc291b4a31c6db0bb4d814","tid":1577141,"uid":60405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:27:24.000Z","msg":"頭先搭巴士經過深水埗又一堆消防&amp;狗車<br />\n啲人係咁望上面 咩事&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:28:07.000Z","msg":"係咪恩福堂個一邊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:30:19.000Z","msg":"今晚好似深水埗有放映會"},{"pid":"3202d29b4aa4f619f724e4f02e16eaa52b